#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a multinomial distribution."
msgstr "从多项分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:3 of
msgid ""
"The multinomial distribution is a multivariate generalisation of the "
"binomial distribution.  Take an experiment with one of ``p`` possible "
"outcomes.  An example of such an experiment is throwing a dice, where the"
" outcome can be 1 through 6.  Each sample drawn from the distribution "
"represents `n` such experiments.  Its values, ``X_i = [X_0, X_1, ..., "
"X_p]``, represent the number of times the outcome was ``i``."
msgstr ""
"多项分布是二项分布的多元推广。考虑一个有 ``p`` 种可能结果的实验，例如"
"掷骰子，其结果可以是 1 到 6。从该分布中抽取的每个样本代表 `n` 次这样的"
"实验。其值 ``X_i = [X_0, X_1, ..., X_p]`` 表示结果为 ``i`` 的次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:11 of
msgid "Number of experiments."
msgstr "实验次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:13 of
msgid ""
"Probabilities of each of the ``p`` different outcomes.  These should sum "
"to 1 (however, the last element is always assumed to account for the "
"remaining probability, as long as ``sum(pvals[:-1]) <= 1)``."
msgstr ""
"每种 ``p`` 个不同结果的概率。它们的总和应为 1（不过只要 ``sum(pvals[:-1])"
" <= 1``，最后一个元素总是被假定为占剩余概率）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:18 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。默认为 None，此时返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:22 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上的期望分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:24 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:26 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:29 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The drawn samples, of shape *size*, if that was provided.  If "
"not, the shape is ``(N,)``.  In other words, each entry "
"``out[i,j,...,:]`` is an N-dimensional value drawn from the distribution."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 抽取的样本，形状为 *size*（如果提供了该参数）。否则，形状为 ``"
"(N,)``。换句话说，每个条目 ``out[i,j,...,:]`` 是从分布中抽取的一个 N 维值"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:29 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The drawn samples, of shape *size*, if that was provided.  If "
"not, the shape is ``(N,)``."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 抽取的样本，如果提供了 *size* 参数，则形状为 *size*。如果没有"
"提供，则形状为 ``(N,)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:32 of
msgid ""
"In other words, each entry ``out[i,j,...,:]`` is an N-dimensional value "
"drawn from the distribution."
msgstr "换句话说，每个条目 ``out[i,j,...,:]`` 是从分布中抽取的 N 维值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:37 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:38 of
msgid "Throw a dice 20 times:"
msgstr "掷骰子 20 次："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:45 of
msgid "It landed 4 times on 1, once on 2, etc."
msgstr "结果中 1 出现了 4 次，2 出现了 1 次，等等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:47 of
msgid "Now, throw the dice 20 times, and 20 times again:"
msgstr "现在，掷骰子 20 次，再掷 20 次："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:53 of
msgid ""
"For the first run, we threw 3 times 1, 4 times 2, etc.  For the second, "
"we threw 2 times 1, 4 times 2, etc."
msgstr ""
"第一次掷骰，1 出现了 3 次，2 出现了 4 次，等等。第二次掷骰，1 出现了 2 次"
"，2 出现了 4 次，等等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:56 of
msgid "A loaded die is more likely to land on number 6:"
msgstr "一个灌铅的骰子更可能落在数字 6 上："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:61 of
msgid ""
"The probability inputs should be normalized. As an implementation detail,"
" the value of the last entry is ignored and assumed to take up any "
"leftover probability mass, but this should not be relied on. A biased "
"coin which has twice as much weight on one side as on the other should be"
" sampled like so:"
msgstr ""
"概率输入应进行归一化。作为实现细节，最后一个值将被忽略，并被假定占据任何"
"剩余的概率质量，但不应依赖于此。一枚偏向一边的硬币（某一侧的权重是另一侧"
"的两倍）应这样采样："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multinomial.multinomial:70 of
msgid "not like:"
msgstr "而不是这样："

